name: Commutes #2
description:
Fluid paint rose from the wall, one crimson wash seeping onto the table with a perfect match to the pixel, dripping and fizzing with the sound of breaking glass.
digital & acrylic on paper
740x800 px
PNG

A collection of digital hand drawings while commuting to work. This is done mostly in my android phone. Falling down the rabbit hole of one's self and looking at people.
